sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant CLI as rhai-cli<br/>(kubectl-odh)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem
    participant GH as raw.githubusercontent.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Admin,GH: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli lint --from=2.x --to=3.x<br/>[--output json|yaml|table]
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET datascienceclusters<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kubeconfig)
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC resource (version detection)
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET dscinitializations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSCI resource (platform init state)

    loop 30+ Sequential Lint Checks
        Note right of CLI: CanApply: semver check<br/>(version applicability)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET/LIST target CRDs<br/>(Notebooks, ISVCs, Kueue,<br/>ServingRuntimes, DSPA, etc.)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>CLI: Resource data
        Note right of CLI: Validate: condition-based<br/>DiagnosticResult
    end

    CLI-->>Admin: DiagnosticResult table/JSON/YAML<br/>Exit code: 0=OK, 1=BLOCKING, 2=ADVISORY

    Note over Admin,GH: Flow 2: Workload Backup

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli backup --output-dir=/backups<br/>[--include notebooks,inferenceservices]
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST workloads across namespaces<br/>(Notebooks, ISVCs, RayClusters, etc.)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Workload resources

    loop Dependency Resolution (per workload)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET referenced ConfigMaps,<br/>PVCs, Secrets<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>CLI: Dependency resources
    end

    CLI->>FS: Write YAML manifests<br/>to --output-dir (0644 perms)
    CLI-->>Admin: Backup summary (count, output path)

    Note over Admin,GH: Flow 3: Dependency Installation

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli deps install [--refresh]

    opt --refresh flag
        CLI->>GH: GET odh-gitops/values.yaml<br/>Auth: None
        GH-->>CLI: Dependency manifest YAML
    end

    Note right of CLI: Validate catalog source<br/>against allowlist:<br/>redhat-operators,<br/>community-operators,<br/>certified-operators,<br/>redhat-marketplace

    Note right of CLI: Reject system namespaces:<br/>kube-*, openshift-*

    CLI->>K8sAPI: CREATE Namespace,<br/>OperatorGroup, Subscription<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Resources created

    loop Poll CSV Status (5s interval, 3 concurrent)
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterServiceVersion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>CLI: CSV status (Pending → Installing → Succeeded)
    end

    CLI-->>Admin: Installation summary<br/>(operator status table)

    Note over Admin,GH: Flow 4: Status / Health Check

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli status
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSC, DSCI, Component CRs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Platform resources

    par 8 Concurrent Health Sections
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET operator pods, deployments<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>CLI: Resource status
    end

    CLI-->>Admin: Health status table<br/>with envelope output

    Note over Admin,GH: Flow 5: Log Aggregation

    Admin->>CLI: rhai-cli logs [--component kserve]
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST/WATCH pods in operator namespace<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Pod list with containers

    par Multi-Container Log Streaming
        CLI->>K8sAPI: GET pods/log<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>CLI: Log stream (chunked)
    end

    CLI-->>Admin: Aggregated logs (stdout)
